<h2 class="center underline", style="font-size:1.9em; font-weight: bold;"> Volunteer Opportunities</h2>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>Volunteer in case of an immigration enforcement (donating food, preparing and serving food, translating)</li>
      <li>Volunteer as an interpreter or translator for Spanish or French</li>
      <li>Volunteer as part of your career as a Grinnell College student</li>
      <li>There are various committees within the organization you could also volunteer to serve on. Please contact us with your skills and interests if you are interested.</li>
      <li>To volunteer, please email us with your skills and availability and best way to contact you.</li>
    </ul>
